<li id="cite_note-48"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-48">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.un.org/en/events/englishlanguageday/">"English Language Day at the United Nations, 23 April 2011"</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.un.org/en/events/englishlanguageday/">http://www.un.org/en/events/englishlanguageday/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2011-07-26</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-49"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.un.org/apps/newsFr/storyF.asp?NewsID=24785&Cr=France&Cr1=">"L'ONU célèbre la Journée de la langue française"</a> (in French). 2011-03-21<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.un.org/apps/newsFr/storyF.asp?NewsID=24785&Cr=France&Cr1=">http://www.un.org/apps/newsFr/storyF.asp?NewsID=24785&amp;Cr=France&amp;Cr1=</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2011-07-26</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-50"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-50">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.un.int/wcm/content/site/portal/cache/offonce/home/pid/22000">"Spanish Language Day to be celebrated at HQ on Tuesday, 12 October 2010"</a>. deleGATE. 2010-10-11<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.un.int/wcm/content/site/portal/cache/offonce/home/pid/22000">http://www.un.int/wcm/content/site/portal/cache/offonce/home/pid/22000</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2011-07-26</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-51"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-51">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0018/001874/187429e.pdf">"Rules of Procedure of the General Conference"</a>. 2010<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0018/001874/187429e.pdf">http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0018/001874/187429e.pdf</a></span>.</span>, Rule 54</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-52"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-52">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.upu.int/en/the-upu/languages.html">"Universal Postal Union — Languages"</a>. Universal Postal Union<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.upu.int/en/the-upu/languages.html">http://www.upu.int/en/the-upu/languages.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2010-08-03</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-53"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-53">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ifad.org/pub/basic/gc/e/!05govco.pdf">"Rules of Procedure of the Governing Council"</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.ifad.org/pub/basic/gc/e/!05govco.pdf">http://www.ifad.org/pub/basic/gc/e/!05govco.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2010-08-03</span>.</span>, Rule 20</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-54"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-54">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ifad.org/pub/basic/eb/e/!06exboa.pdf">"Rules of Procedure of the Executive Board"</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.ifad.org/pub/basic/eb/e/!06exboa.pdf">http://www.ifad.org/pub/basic/eb/e/!06exboa.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2010-08-03</span>.</span>, Rule 26</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
